{
  "id": "69a61388063d2df293bf6c9a",
  "title": "正規表現というもの",
  "created": 1772491657,
  "updated": 1772493281,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a61388063d2df293bf6c9a",
      "text": "正規表現というもの",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b874",
      "text": "from [ふーことましろとひよりの会話]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b875",
      "text": "[正規表現]というもの",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491675
    },
    {
      "id": "69a6139f000000000059b8f8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491679,
      "updated": 1772491679
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b876",
      "text": " ざっと見たところ、特に間違っているところはないみたい（あったら教えて）[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491679
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b877",
      "text": " 　これは女子高生の会話じゃないという批判は、概ねその通り",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b878",
      "text": " 　　説明のためのウソだね",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b879",
      "text": " 　今後、こういう生成AIベースのコンテンツを量産しても問題ないかな？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b87a",
      "text": " 　　もちろん、正確性のチェックはする前提として",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b87b",
      "text": " はじめは文章が多くて読みづらいと感じたが、今読んでみるとなんか面白かった[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b87c",
      "text": "  これで足りなくて、状態遷移マシンを実装するところが第2話かな？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b87d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b87e",
      "text": "code:txt",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b87f",
      "text": " あなたはプロの脚本家です。以下の3人で、「正規表現」というテーマについて対話（鼎談）を作成してください。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b880",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b881",
      "text": "――放課後の教室。ノートPCを囲む三人。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b882",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b883",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「はいはーい、今日のテーマは〜……“正規表現”！ でたよ、呪文みたいなやつ。なんか ^ とか $ とか、顔文字かよって感じのアレね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b884",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b885",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「ふふ、最初はびっくりしますよね。記号がたくさん並んでいて、暗号みたいで……。でも、仕組みがわかると、ちゃんと意味があるんですよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b886",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b887",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「定義からいこう。正規表現は“文字のパターンを表すための記法”。大量の文章の中から、特定の形をした文字列を見つけたり、置き換えたりするための道具」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b888",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b889",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「つまり、“文字の型抜き”ってこと？ クッキー型みたいな？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b88a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b88b",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「概ね正しい。型に合う文字列だけを抽出する。例えば“メールアドレスっぽい形”とか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b88c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b88d",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「ああ、フォーム入力で“正しいメール形式で入力してください”って出るの、あれですよね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b88e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b88f",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「あー！ あれ正規表現か！ いきなり身近になったわ。急に親近感わいたんだけど」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b890",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b891",
      "text": "[** 記号って何してるの？]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b892",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b893",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「でもさ、なんであんな記号まみれなの？ \\d+ とか、もう圧がすごい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b894",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b895",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「圧はある。でも合理的。“\\d”は数字ひとつ。“+”は“ひとつ以上続く”。だから“\\d+”で“数字が1個以上続く”」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b896",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b897",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「は？ それだけ？ じゃあ“123”とか“9”とかもOKってこと？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b898",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b899",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「そう」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b89a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b89b",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「あ、だから電話番号とか、注文番号のチェックに使えるんですね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b89c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b89d",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「なるほどね〜。じゃあ ^ と $ は？ いつも端っこにいるアイツら」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b89e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b89f",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「開始と終了を表す。“^”は“ここから始まる”。“$”は“ここで終わる”。つまり全文一致させたいときに使う」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8a0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8a1",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「あー！ 途中に数字があるだけじゃダメで、“全部が数字だけ”にしたいときに必要なのか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8a2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8a3",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「理解が早い」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8a4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8a5",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「ふーこちゃん、ちゃんと整理できてますよ。すごいです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8a7",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「え、なに急にほめモード？ 伸びるよわたし」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8a8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8a9",
      "text": "[** 正規表現のヤバさ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8ab",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「でもさ、正規表現って“読めないコード代表”みたいな扱いされがちじゃん？ “書いた本人しかわからん”みたいな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8ad",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「それは事実。複雑に書けば可読性は下がる。設計が重要」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8ae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8af",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「わかります……。便利だからといって、ぎゅっと一行に詰め込むと、あとから見る人が困りますよね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8b0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8b1",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「わかる〜！ 未来の自分がいちばん敵になるやつね。“なんでこんな書き方したん？”ってなる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8b2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8b3",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「対策はある。コメントを書く。段階的にテストする。必要以上に欲張らない」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8b4",
      "text": "\t[正規表現を欲張らない]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8b5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8b6",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「欲張らない大事。なんか“全部まとめて一発でやったる！”ってなりがちなんだよね。ロマン砲みたいな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8b7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8b8",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「ロマン砲は暴発する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8b9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8ba",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「ふふ……言い方がちょっと怖いです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8bb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8bc",
      "text": "[** じゃあ、使う意味ある？]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8bd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8be",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「正直さ、ちょっとした文字探しなら普通に検索でよくない？ って思うときある」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8bf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8c0",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「単純検索では無理なケースがある。“形は似てるけど内容が毎回違う”場合」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8c1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8c2",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「例えば？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8c3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8c4",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「“2026-03-02”のような日付。年も月も日も変わる。でも“数字4桁-数字2桁-数字2桁”という形は同じ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8c5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8c6",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「あー、それを一気に拾えるのか。確かに便利」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8c7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8c8",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「ログ解析やデータ整理では必須レベル」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8c9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8ca",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「つまり……地味だけど、裏方としてとても強い存在なんですね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8cb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8cc",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「縁の下の力持ち系スキルってことか。派手じゃないけど、使える人かっこいいやつ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8cd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8ce",
      "text": "[** 結局どう向き合う？]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8d0",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「じゃあさ、初心者はどうやって仲良くなればいいの？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8d1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8d2",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「全部覚えようとしない。まずは“数字”“文字”“繰り返し”の三つだけ理解する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8d3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8d4",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「少しずつ、ですね。いきなり難しいものに挑まなくていいんです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8d5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8d6",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「[スモールスタート]大事、と。いきなりラスボス行くなってことね」",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772493281
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8d8",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「そう。あと、テストサイトを使う。実際に文字を入れて、どこにマッチするか目で確認する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8d9",
      "text": " [正規表現を可視化してくれるサイト]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8da",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8db",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「あ、それいい。目で見えると安心するわ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8dc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8dd",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「成功体験があると、怖さが減りますものね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8de",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8df",
      "text": "[** まとめ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8e0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8e1",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「というわけで！ 正規表現は――」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8e2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8e3",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「“文字の型を定義する道具”」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8e4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8e5",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「“怖そうに見えて、実はとても実用的な味方”ですね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8e6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8e7",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「最初は記号の圧にビビるけど、仕組みがわかればただの型抜き職人。ロマン砲にせず、丁寧に使えば最強。って感じか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8e8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8e9",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「妥当な結論」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8ea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8eb",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「ふふ、今日もいいお話でしたね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8ec",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8ed",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「よーし、じゃあ次回は“配列”とかいっちゃう？ みんなついてこいよ〜？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8ee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8ef",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「段階的に」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8f0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8f1",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「やさしくお願いしますね、進行係さん」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8f2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8f3",
      "text": "――チャイムが鳴る。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8f4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8f5",
      "text": "正規表現という呪文は、少しだけ身近なものになった。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a61389000000000059b8f7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772491657,
      "updated": 1772491657
    }
  ]
}